{"type":"message","id":"67b8a216","parentId":"7206e9d2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:54:43.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so I'm starting fresh:\n- SOUL.md is general guidelines about how to be\n- USER.md is empty (no name, no context)\n- IDENTITY.md is empty (just a template)\n- MEMORY.md doesn't exist yet (fresh session)\n- Today's and yesterday's memory files don't exist yet\n\nThis is literally the first session. Let me greet the human and figure out who they are and who I am. I should be conversational but not robotic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. Just came online.\n\nWho am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7-flashx","usage":{"input":9987,"output":214,"cacheRead":1240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108463698}}
