{"type":"message","id":"0bc46208","parentId":"7f8dcc67","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:53:06.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要执行一个完整流程：\n1. 先让小车走到红色物品位置\n2. 然后原地转圈\n3. 然后回到起点\n\n我之前尝试让 approach_color 自动完成返程，但失败了。现在需要分开执行：\n1. 靠近红色目标（disable-spin-after-reach, no-return-to-start）\n2. 等待到达后，手动转圈\n3. 然后导航回起点\n\n让我先重新执行靠近红色目标的命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我分步执行：先靠近红色目标，然后转圈，最后导航回起点。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cd193bae0a6449139413f726","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/skills/ROS-limo-car && conda run -n mqtt-server python3 scripts/limo_ws_client.py --host 172.31.94.183 --port 8765 approach_color --color red --camera-topic /usb_cam_0/image_raw --linear-x 0.12 --slow-linear-x 0.06 --min-area 100 --stop-distance 0.25 --stop-area-ratio 0.008 --stop-min-area 1000 --max-steps 600 --disable-spin-after-reach --no-return-to-start --debug-output /tmp/limo_red_final.jpg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7-flashx","usage":{"input":17596,"output":372,"cacheRead":2792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774111964894}}
